[
    {
        "content": "<p>I'm currently reading the code of <code>simp</code>, and I noticed that in <code>Lean.Meta.Simp.main</code>, <code>methods</code> is converted to <code>MethodsRef</code>, as shown in <code>Code Snippet 1</code>; then in <code>Lean.Meta.Simp.simpLoop</code>, <code>getMethods</code> converts <code>MethodsRef</code> back to <code>Methods</code>, as shown in <code>Code Snippet 2</code>. </p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\">-- Code Snippet 1</span>\n<span class=\"bp\">#</span><span class=\"n\">check</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Lean</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">Meta</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">Simp</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">main</span>\n<span class=\"kn\">def</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">main</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">e</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Expr</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">ctx</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Context</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">stats</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Stats</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">{})</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">methods</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Methods</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">{})</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">MetaM</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">Result</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">×</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Stats</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">do</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"k\">let</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ctx</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ctx</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">with</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">config</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">←</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ctx</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">config</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">updateArith</span><span class=\"o\">),</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">lctxInitIndices</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">←</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">getLCtx</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">numIndices</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">}</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">withSimpContext</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ctx</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">do</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"c1\">-- Here, methods converted to `MethodsRef`</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">let</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">r</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">s</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">←</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">go</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">e</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">methods</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">toMethodsRef</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ctx</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">|&gt;.</span><span class=\"n\">run</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">stats</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">with</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">}</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">trace</span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">Meta</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">Tactic</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">simp</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">numSteps</span><span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">\"{s.numSteps}\"</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">return</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">r</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">s</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">with</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">})</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\">-- Code Snippet 2</span>\n<span class=\"bp\">#</span><span class=\"n\">check</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Lean</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">Meta</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">Simp</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">simpLoop</span>\n<span class=\"kn\">def</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">getMethods</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">SimpM</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Methods</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">return</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">MethodsRef</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">toMethods</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">←</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">read</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"c1\">-- Here, MethodsRef is converted to `Methods`</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p><strong>I'm confused about why <code>MethodsRef</code> is passed in <code>SimpM</code> instead of directly passing <code>Methods</code>?</strong> As far as I know, <code>MethodsRef.toMethodsImpl</code> converts <code>MethodsRef</code> to <code>Methods</code> directly through <code>unsafeCast</code>, which suggests that the underlying data representation is the same. So why define a <code>MethodsRef</code>? </p>\n<p><strong>Moreover, I don't understand the definition of</strong> <code>MethodsRef</code>: </p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">private</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kn\">opaque</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">MethodsRefPointed</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">NonemptyType</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"o\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">private</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kn\">def</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">MethodsRef</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">Type</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">MethodsRefPointed</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">type</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">instance</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Nonempty</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">MethodsRef</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">MethodsRefPointed</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">property</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>This definition seems a bit strange, especially for <code>opaque</code> and <code>NonemptyType.{0}</code>.</p>",
